      "span_id": "p156_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0002",
      "text": " 137",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0003",
      "text": "types have been attempted.  If all supported SOF types have been attempted and the Fabric has re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        540.09,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0004",
      "text": "jected all or timed out, the Fabric and Nx_Port are incompatible and outside intervention is required.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        536.57,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0005",
      "text": "The Fabric shall remove all Class 1, and 6 connections to an N_Port when the N_Port performs a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        539.89,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0006",
      "text": "Fabric Login.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        153.7,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0007",
      "text": "6.2.4",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        118.22,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0008",
      "text": "Frequency",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        130.97,
        178.76,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0009",
      "text": "Login between an Nx_Port and the Fabric should be long-lived.  If Implicit Logout with the Fabric has",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        540.08,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0010",
      "text": "occurred, it is necessary to perform a new Login with the Fabric (see 6.4.4",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        423.71,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0011",
      "text": ").",
      "bbox": [
        433.71,
        166.96,
        439.78,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0012",
      "text": "6.2.5",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        118.24,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0013",
      "text": "Fabric Login completion - Originator",
      "bbox": [
        128.24,
        190.96,
        301.48,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
