      "text": "b) in Class 2, the Originator has transmitted the ACK (EOF",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        262.97,
        370.16,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0021",
      "text": "t",
      "bbox": [
        370.14,
        264.76,
        372.36,
        273.66
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0022",
      "text": ") to the LS_ACC, or",
      "bbox": [
        372.36,
        262.97,
        459.54,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0023",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        286.97,
        114.38,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0024",
      "text": "in Class 3, the Originator has received the LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        286.97,
        352.94,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0025",
      "text": "When Login is ended, the values of buffer-to-buffer Credit are initialized.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.97,
        414.35,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0026",
      "text": "6.2.6",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        118.22,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
