      "text": "a) in Class 1, the Responder has received the ACK (EOF",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        382.96,
        363.47,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0030",
      "text": "t",
      "bbox": [
        363.48,
        384.76,
        365.7,
        393.66
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0031",
      "text": " or EOF",
      "bbox": [
        365.7,
        382.97,
        400.67,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0032",
      "text": "dt",
      "bbox": [
        400.68,
        384.76,
        407.34,
        393.66
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 4
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0033",
      "text": ") to the LS_ACC, or",
      "bbox": [
        407.34,
        382.97,
        494.52,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 5
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0034",
      "text": "b) in Class 2, the Responder has received the ACK (EOF",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        406.97,
        363.47,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0035",
      "text": "t",
      "bbox": [
        363.48,
        408.76,
        365.7,
        417.66
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0036",
      "text": ") to the LS_ACC, or",
      "bbox": [
        365.7,
        406.97,
        452.86,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0037",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        430.97,
        114.38,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0038",
      "text": "in Class 3, the Responder has transmitted the LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.97,
        369.58,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0039",
      "text": "When Fabric Login has ended successfully, the values of buffer-to-buffer Credit are initialized.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.97,
        510.38,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0040",
      "text": "6.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.97,
        109.88,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0041",
      "text": "N_Port Login",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        478.97,
        182.61,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0042",
      "text": "6.3.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        118.22,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0043",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        502.96,
        186.53,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0044",
      "text": "N_Port Login follows the Fabric Login procedure.  If a Fabric is present, as determined by performing",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.98,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0045",
      "text": "the Fabric Login procedure, an Nx_Port proceeds with N_Port Login according to 6.3.2.2.  If a Fabric",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        540.01,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0046",
      "text": "is not present, as determined by performing the Fabric Login procedure, an Nx_Port proceeds with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        539.84,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0047",
      "text": "N_Port Login according to 6.3.2.4.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        247.61,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0048",
      "text": "N_Port Login accomplishes the following functions:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        321.4,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0049",
      "text": "a) It provides each Nx_Port with the other Nx_Port's operating characteristics, N_Port_Name and",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        610.96,
        539.98,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 23,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0050",
      "text": "Node_Name.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        622.96,
        181.26,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 23,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0051",
      "text": "b) If a Fabric is not present, it assigns the native N_Port_ID for both Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        647.02,
        455.81,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 24,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0052",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        671.02,
        114.38,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 25,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p156_s0053",
      "text": "If initializes the Nx_Port end-to-end Credit.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        671.02,
        310.14,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 25,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    }
